1.	Problem Statement:
The objective of the EduAccess Hub project is to create a user-friendly educational website that provides easy access to study materials, online courses, tutorials Many students face difficulty in finding quality educational resources, study materials, video lectures, and useful websites in one place. They often spend a lot of time searching across different platforms. EduAccess Hub solves this problem by providing a single platform where students can easily access learning resources.

2. Project Objective:
The objective of the EduAccess Hub project is to create a user-friendly educational website that provides easy access to study materials, online courses, tutorials , videos, and useful learning resources. The website aims to save students' time and improve their learning experience.

3. Solution Description:
EduAccess Hub is a web application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides an organized interface where users can browse educational resources, access learning materials, and navigate easily through different sections. The responsive design ensures that the website works smoothly on desktops and mobile devices.
