•	Selected SDG: SDG 4 – Quality Education:
What the SDG focuses on: SDG 4 aims to ensure inclusive, equitable, and quality education for everyone. It promotes lifelong learning opportunities and equal access to educational resources.
Why this issue is important: Many students do not have easy access to quality study materials, online courses, and learning resources. A single platform can make education more accessible and improve learning outcomes.

2. Problem Statement:
What is the problem? Students often struggle to find reliable educational resources in one place. They have to visit multiple websites, which is time-consuming and confusing.
Where does this problem exist? This problem exists in schools, colleges, and among self-learning students, especially in rural and remote areas.
Who is affected? Students, teachers, and learners who depend on online educational resources.
Why is it serious? Lack of easy access to quality resources affects learning, wastes time, and reduces productivity.
What could happen if it is not solved? Students may miss learning opportunities, become less productive, and face difficulty in improving their skills.

3. Proposed Solution:
What your project is EduAccess Hub is a web application that provides educational resources, study materials, tutorials, and useful learning links in one place.
How the system works Users visit the website, browse different learning categories, and access educational content through a simple and user-friendly interface.
How it helps solve the problem It saves time by organizing educational resources on a single platform, making learning easier and more accessible.
Who will use the application Students, teachers, self-learners, and anyone interested in improving their knowledge.

4. Project Features:
Responsive Design: Works smoothly on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
Easy Navigation: Simple menu to access different educational sections.
Educational Resources: Provides study materials, tutorials, and learning links.
Interactive User Interface: Clean and attractive interface built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
Fast Access: Users can quickly find the information they need.
User-Friendly Layout: Easy to understand and use for learners of all levels.

